@node Settings Profiles
@subsection Settings Profiles

It can be rather annoying when switching between multiple sets of coherent settings.  For example@comma{} it is tedious to change from a live demonstration style setup to a full-screen projector slide show style setup.  One set of hooks cannot do the job.

@node Recording Integration
@subsection Recording Integration

Whenever you change the resolution of a frame for recording@comma{} you need to configure the output resolution in OBS@.  To start recording@comma{} you have to click on OBS@.  This kind of work could be tighter and integrated into @code{moc-dispatch}.

